  "title": "feat(slider): allow setting which Pits to show  ",
  "body": "A prop `valuesToShow={[0, 50, 100]}` allows you to specify which percentages to show. The annoying part is that not for every % a Pit is rendered. The values are:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nconst pitValues = [0, 3, 6, 9, 12, 15, 18, 21, 24, 26, 29, 32, 35, 38, 41, 44, 47, 50, 53, 56, 59, 62, 65, 68, 71, 74, 76, 79, 82, 85, 88, 91, 94, 97, 100];\r\n```\r\n\r\nI'm not sure what to make of it.\r\n\r\nrelated to #2276\r\n\r\nOnly for review since I continued on #2276",
